Suspected Gunmen have attacked Malufashi local government of Katsina state, where they shot death one Umar Isah Funtua, a lecturer of School of Basic and Remedial Studies (SBRS). information gathered revealed that the gunmen entered the town with sophisticated weapons on Monday 5th, January, 2020, around 10pm shooting sporadically as residents ran for their dear lives. the residents later discovered that
“they shot and killed a lecturer of SBRS funtua by name Umar isah funtua.. may his soul rest in peace amin”. Meanwhile, the state Police Public Relation Officer, Gambo Isah, siad he is not aware with the attack, but will gets detail information of the happening by tomorrow.